scilib.objects

Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • scilib.objects.Group

  • public class Group
extends Object
    Organizer which manages TeamData objects.

    You can add and remove TeamData objects to this object, and set filters and sorters to organize them.

    TeamData objects which are being filtered and sorted are part of the TeamData pool. TeamData objects from the pool which have passed through the Sorter and Filter are part of the active TeamData list.

    Author:
    Auxiliatrix
